latestIgtvVideos.title: This Rakhi, It’s #BestSaidWithSkinn
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My sister @dewangana_chhillar and I don’t get to spend as much time as we used to when we were younger, and I miss having her around. So, this Rakhi we decided to spend some time together and guess what?! I even planned for a carefully selected surprise to express how special she is to me.

So go ahead and make your sibling’s day this #RakshaBhandhan. Because for the ones who always have your back, it’s #BestSaidWithSkinn!

I would love to hear your sibling stories, so go ahead and share them on @skinn_titan page with the hashtag #BestSaidWithSKINN and stand a chance to win exciting hampers for you and your sibling!

#SKINN

latestIgtvVideos.title: Menstrual Hygiene Day (Throwback)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#ThrowbackThursday 
On World Menstrual Hygiene Day, remembering the initial phases of my project. Who knew one day we would gain the support of governments and organisations all across the world. Today I look back at these fond memories and feel proud of how far we’ve come.
Project Shakti was an idea that gave shape to my vision and if we put our minds to it, the youth can definitely change the world. Thank you @shariq_patel and @missindiaorg
